h d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 10h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 10h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path></svg> <!-- -->Department</label><div class=\"relative\"><select id=\"department\" name=\"department\" class=\"w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 focus:border-brand-blue focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-50 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-slate-800 text-sm placeholder:text-slate-400 focus:outline-none transition-all duration-200 shadow-sm appearance-none pr-10 cursor-pointer\"><option value=\"\" disabled=\"\" selected=\"\">Select department</option><option value=\"AIDS\">AIDS</option><option value=\"AIML\">AIML</option><option value=\"BBA\">BBA</option><option value=\"BCS/MCS\">BCS/MCS</option><option value=\"CSE\">CSE</option><option value=\"CY\">CY</option><option value=\"Integrated B.Tech\">Integrated B.Tech</option><option value=\"Integrated M.Tech\">Integrated M.Tech</option><option value=\"M.Com\">M.Com</option><option value=\"MBA\">MBA</option><option value=\"MCA/BCA\">MCA/BCA</option></select><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 pointer-events-none\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"min-h-[16px]\"></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><label for=\"position\" class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-briefcase w-3.5 h-3.5 text-brand-blue\"><path d=\"M16 20V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16\"></path><rect width=\"20\" height=\"14\" x=\"2\" y=\"6\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg> <!-- -->Position</label><div class=\"relative\"><select id=\"position\" name=\"position\" class=\"w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 focus:border-brand-blue focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-50 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-slate-800 text-sm placeholder:text-slate-400 focus:outline-none transition-all duration-200 shadow-sm appearance-none pr-10 cursor-pointer\"><option value=\"\" disabled=\"\" selected=\"\">Select position</option><option value=\"Goalkeeper (GK)\">Goalkeeper (GK)</option><option value=\"Defender (CD)\">Defender (CD)</option><option value=\"Defender (RD/LD)\">Defender (RD/LD)</option><option value=\"Midfielder (CM)\">Midfielder (CM)</option><option value=\"Midfielder (DM)\">Midfielder (DM)</option><option value=\"Midfielder (AM)\">Midfielder (AM)</option><option value=\"Winger (RW/LW)\">Winger (RW/LW)</option><option value=\"Forward (ST)\">Forward (ST)</option></select><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 pointer-events-none\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"min-h-[16px]\"></div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><label for=\"contact\" class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-phone w-3.5 h-3.5 text-brand-blue\"><path d=\"M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z\"></path></svg> <!-- -->Mobile Number</label><input id=\"contact\" type=\"tel\" placeholder=\"10-digit number\" maxLength=\"10\" class=\"w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 focus:border-brand-blue focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-50 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-slate-800 text-sm placeholder:text-slate-400 focus:outline-none transition-all duration-200 shadow-sm\" name=\"contact\" value=\"\"/><div class=\"min-h-[16px]\"></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><label for=\"statement\" class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text w-3.5 h-3.5 text-brand-blue\"><path d=\"M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg> <!-- -->Brief Statement (Optional)</label><textarea id=\"statement\" name=\"statement\" rows=\"4\" placeholder=\"Tell us about your football experience and why you want to join...\" class=\"w-full bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 focus:border-brand-blue focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-50 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 text-slate-800 text-sm placeholder:text-slate-400 focus:outline-none transition-all duration-200 shadow-sm resize-none\"></textarea><div class=\"text-right text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 mt-1\">0<!-- -->/500</div><div class=\"min-h-[16px]\"></div></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn-blue w-full justify-center !py-4 !text-base mt-2 shadow-lg \" tabindex=\"0\">Submit Application</button><p class=\"text-slate-400 text-[11px] font-medium text-center\">Your information is used solely for trial selection purposes.</p></form></div></section></div><!--/$--></div></main><footer class=\"bg-brand-blue-dark border-t